{"tid":2209124,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中美角力｜美議員提案授權動武護台 倡美國總統訪問台灣","createTime":"2020-09-19T11:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T05:26:42.000Z","uid":239336,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7a1d60b187296faad979ec1d3774b7543cdd82bf","tid":2209124,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"美國國務次卿克拉奇（Keith Krach）率團到台灣出席今日的已故台灣前總統李登輝的告別禮拜，北京立即加強武力恫嚇，僅昨日即派出最少18架次軍機擾台，更3度越過台灣海峽中線，令台海局勢空前升溫。美國共和黨參議員斯科特（Rick Scott）提出《防止台灣遭侵略法案》（Taiwan Invasion Prevention Act），授權美國總統在大陸武力犯台時得動用武力防衞台灣，法案並鼓勵總統與國務卿訪台。<br />\n<br />\n繼多位參議員星期四（17日）在外委會聽證會上表達對北京恫嚇台灣的關注、要求美國以實際作為協助台灣抗衡中國壓力後，斯科特同日於Twitter 宣佈，向國會提出《防止台灣遭侵略法案》，以表達對台灣安全的關注及美國國會對台灣的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200919/SEWRWU56OZHNXM4V3IWDYOCYFA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1dIsDrp5Ug9Fu1bKfr9fIihM-1DfH4cvdIcJwswbzVWjJwtKf_MeHireg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200919%2FSEWRWU56OZHNXM4V3IWDYOCYFA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1dIsDrp5Ug9Fu1bKfr9fIihM-1DfH4cvdIcJwswbzVWjJwtKf_MeHireg&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE4m5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=b1c7a734\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200919%2FSEWRWU56OZHNXM4V3IWDYOCYFA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1dIsDrp5Ug9Fu1bKfr9fIihM-1DfH4cvdIcJwswbzVWjJwtKf_MeHireg&h=fd84806a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200919/SEWRWU56OZHNXM4V3IWDYOCYFA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1dIsDrp5Ug9Fu1bKfr9fIihM-1DfH4cvdIcJwswbzVWjJwtKf_MeHireg</a>"},{"pid"